# Figures/ contents are recreatable too, but the map PNG is a committed exception (safe to share, worked example).
Figures/*
!Figures/.gitkeep
!Figures/registrants_map.png

# Depends on the gitignored raw xlsx, so it can't run for anyone who only has this repo -- kept local only.
